551
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:48,780
f-friendship,

552
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:51,370
or love.

553
00:36:53,100 --> 00:36:56,690
But, I just...

554
00:36:58,050 --> 00:36:59,810
I just...

555
00:37:02,530 --> 00:37:04,520
am happy...

556
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:10,740
I'm just happy to receive the love...

557
00:37:11,460 --> 00:37:13,390
you showered upon me.

558
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:17,390
It was warm...

559
00:37:19,490 --> 00:37:22,030
and comforting.

560
00:37:23,240 --> 00:37:24,940
That's why...

561
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:29,830
I'd like to be beside you

562
00:37:32,100 --> 00:37:34,570
